{"data":[{"date":"18:12 13/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 19 V-League: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/20/truoc-vong-19-vleague-co-hoi-cho-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ea1i Pleiku.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u1edf n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i BXH l\u00e0 CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 19 V-League C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 19 V-League C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Truoc-vong-19-V-League-Co-hoi-cho-HAGL-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 v\u1edbi 24 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng th\u00e0nh 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao h\u01a1n khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nhau 2-2 trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea7m t\u00e3 t\u1ea1i C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua khi\u1ebfn C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1eadm 1-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00ean T\u00e2y Nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1m s\u00e1t nhau t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean BXH, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n. \u0110ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 cao nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 4 \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1edbi H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a l\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn bao nhi\u00eau b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC, \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i V-League. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u2018h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t\u2019 CLB TP.HCM v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-3. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u2018t\u1eed th\u1ee7\u2019, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadm l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nam Dinh vs Ha Noi\" title=\"Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/truc-tiep-nam-dinh-vs-ha-noi-18h00-ngay-205-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n g\u00ec Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n xa nh\u00e0 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n 19-8 g\u1eb7p Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN s\u1ebd t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thua, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch S\u00e0i G\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1eeda, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u1eeba \u0111ang b\u1eebng b\u1eebng kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n HAGL (4-2) \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 CLB TP.HCM t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League. \u00a0Ngo\u00e0i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00fap CLB TPHCM t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 18 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 32 b\u00e0n thua - m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t V-League \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \"h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c\" b\u1eb1ng 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi mang t\u00ean Marclei Santos v\u00e0 Matias (c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18), r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Miura s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB SLNA li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u2018ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda\u2019 Vinh g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam? V\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"LTD vong 19 V-League 2018\" title=\"LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/vong-19-v-league.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>LT\u0110 v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4204","checkdouble":"191117"},{"date":"18:55 13/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/30/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte. </strong>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba. </strong>Juventus \u0111ang nung n\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a Paul Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb Man United. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Bianconeri quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Miralem Pjanic. Hi\u1ec7n Pjanic \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft Barcelona t\u1edbi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t \u0111\u00f2i \u0111i, Juve v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cris Ronaldo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo kh\u00f4ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Pogba.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 137 MU c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 137 MU c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/pogba-abou-diaby-con-da-hay-hon-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Modric: \"T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup\". </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo. </strong>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Rodrigo v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi sang Juventus. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Los Blancos trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 9 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Rodrigo\" title=\"tien dao Rodrigo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Rodrigo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t.</strong> Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Jurgen Gede. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i tin \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. </strong>Philipp Lahm ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Die Mannschaft t\u1ef1 tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>James Rodriguez mu\u1ed1n quay l\u1ea1i Real.</strong> James Rodriguez mong mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Julen Lopetegui m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda m\u1eddi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4203","checkdouble":"191118"},{"date":"21:18 13/07","title":"River Plate b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/river-plate-bao-gia-sao-moi-noi-cho-real-madrid-va-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. CLB Argentina c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Tottenham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quintero n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u1edd World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp River Plate d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Porto t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Juan Fernando Quintero. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuintero \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Colombia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, anh ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Los Cafeteros sau 4 tr\u1eadn. D\u00f9 Colombia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i xa nh\u01b0ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn lan t\u1ecfa sang ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/River-Plate-chi-ban-Quintero-voi-gia-25-trieu-Euro-cho-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Quintero ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Anh l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a Quintero v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 19 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>River Plate b\u00e1o gi\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi Porto, River Plate c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 sau World Cup r\u1eb1ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho c\u00e1c CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda River. V\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, Rodolfo D'Onofrio th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang n\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 c\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"quintero River Plate\" title=\"quintero River Plate\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/quintero-River-Plate.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>River Plate ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Quintero v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Quintero. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i River. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Quintero ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, D'Onofrio kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Quintero. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u River so s\u00e1nh anh v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina, Juan Roman Riquelme. \u201cQuintero khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u1edb t\u1edbi Riquelme\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u00f3c quan s\u00e1t t\u1ed1t. Quintero c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra b\u00ean tr\u00e1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4202","checkdouble":"191123"},{"date":"22:28 13/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e1\u201d kh\u1ecfi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb sau World Cup</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 11,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi nay, trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga khi HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u01b0a th\u00edch nh\u1eefng Gerard Pique, Samuel Umtiti r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Thomas Vermaelen h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Mina \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 sau 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Colombia v\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00f9 \u1edf Barcelona hay \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c trong m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Yerry-Mina-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&rdquo;, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia n\u00f3i. &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, v\u00ec CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o d\u00f9 \u1edf Barcelona hay ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMina k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Barcelona m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb HLV Valverde g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n. &ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u00fac t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trong c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn&rdquo;, anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" title=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Yerry-Mina-cua-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u00e0. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qua TV, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c v\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i Barcelona.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 tin Everton \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Mina. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu trung v\u1ec7 cao t\u1edbi 1m94.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-191104.html\">Barca chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea-180-191078.html\">Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea-180-191016.html\">Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-180-190985.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca trong h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-cu-nguoi-den-phap-dam-phan-mua-rabiot-180-190971.html\">Barca c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua sao PSG</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4201","checkdouble":"191127"},{"date":"06:24 14/07","title":"Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/3/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang ch\u1ee7 CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng b\u00e0i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar t\u1eeb PSG?</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi ch\u1ec9 sau v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro sang Paris Saint-Germain. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng, khi Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u0169 Barcelona m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona-180-186568.html\" target=\"_blank\">gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid</span>, kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1n b\u00e3o t\u1ed1 th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Cules.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mua Neymar t\u1eeb PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mua Neymar t\u1eeb PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mua Neymar t\u1eeb PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 Kh\u00f4ng!</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng cao v\u1ecb th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, danh ti\u1ebfng thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh Cristiano Ronaldo, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Bernabeu sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady gi\u1eefa mu\u00f4n tr\u00f9ng v\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, Real Madrid m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Neymar ngay tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 CLB. N\u1ed9i dung b\u00e1c b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Brazil c\u1ee7a Los Blancos c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar, Real Madrid xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn Paris Saint-Germain c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Real v\u00e0 PSG c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00ean n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh giao d\u1ecbch mua b\u00e1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Neymar kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi PSG m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trong khi Real Madrid c\u00f3 l\u1ebd d\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang l\u00e0 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona-180-186568.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-neu-neymar-toi-real-madrid-va-su-run-ray-cua-messilona-180-186568.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Neymar t\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 run r\u1ea9y c\u1ee7a \u201cMessilona\u201d</span><br>\r\nTheo Lionel Messi, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh n\u1ebfu Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Barcelona. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thien-ac-noi-neymar-ca-nhan-da-bao-gio-lon-hon-tap-the-421-190529.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/thien-ac-noi-neymar-ca-nhan-da-bao-gio-lon-hon-tap-the.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thien-ac-noi-neymar-ca-nhan-da-bao-gio-lon-hon-tap-the-421-190529.html\">Thi\u1ec7n \u00e1c n\u01a1i Neymar: C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 bao gi\u1edd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3?</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u0103n th\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1ebfn s\u00faa, ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u1ea5t thanh cao truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng anh h\u00f9ng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y nay. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4200","checkdouble":"191138"},{"date":"19:21 13/07","title":"HLV Emery h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/hlv-emery-hua-hen-arsenal-se-co-them-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 tham v\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 bao g\u1ed3m Lucas Torreira, Bernd Leno, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Matteo Guendouzi v\u00e0 Stephan Lichtsteiner. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Unai Emery t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho nh\u1eefng Per Mertesacker, Jack Wilshere v\u00e0 Santi Cazorla \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/HLV-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lucas Torreira l\u00e0 1 trong 5 t\u00e2n binh Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cH\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1ed5n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i mua b\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. V\u00e0 Emery d\u00f9 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery tro thanh HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery tro thanh HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Arsenal-chieu-mo-Torreira-Tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u00e0 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \"bom t\u1ea5n\"</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 khi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1ecd\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 46 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 xem li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho Arsenal hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Emery tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Boreham Wood cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Singapore d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-hang-hot-ligue-1-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191053.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: H\u00e0ng hot Ligue 1 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\">Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes-172-190877.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wenger-bat-bai-khoi-arsenal-vikante-172-190866.html\">Wenger b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal v\u00ec...Kante?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal-172-190840.html\">T\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4199","checkdouble":"191120"},{"date":"20:00 13/07","title":"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d hy v\u1ecdng uy danh c\u1ee7a si\u00eau t\u00e2n binh Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed1n x\u01b0a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic b\u1ecb chi\u00eau d\u1ee5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus t\u1eeb AS Roma \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2016/17, Miralem Pjanic \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia & Herzegovina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi v\u1eafng \u0111i Pjanic, Juventus l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c lao \u0111ao \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Bianconeri hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Muon-oai-Ronaldo,-Juventus-muon-mua-Pogba-cua-Man-United-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pjanic \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c Pjanic c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Barcelona hay Man City. Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 5 s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juve t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Juventus thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Pjanic \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, h\u1ecd t\u00ednh s\u1eb5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n x\u1ea3y ra. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Pjanic \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Paul Pogba\" title=\"tien ve Paul Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba c\u1ee7a Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Juve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Pjanic v\u1ec1 thay Pogba gia nh\u1eadp M.U v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u chuy\u1ebfn quay l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay kh\u00f4ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh. Anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn Anh t\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Pjanic \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Barca hay Man City, Juventus d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin m\u1edbi chi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus hy v\u1ecdng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Pogba m\u1ee7i l\u00f2ng. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Pjanic (n\u1ebfu anh ra \u0111i) c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz sau 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191085.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec\u2026 Messi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4198","checkdouble":"191121"},{"date":"20:37 13/07","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean r\u1eddi Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/muc-tieu-cua-mu-duoc-khuyen-roi-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mahrez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maguire v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Man City tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Leicester x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Man United \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mahrez ng\u1ee3i ca Maguire</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Maguire ngay trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u01a1i cho Leicester \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. L\u00ean \u0110T Anh, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia 1-2 trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Maguire 1 n\u0103m qua \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a Man United. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Hull City. Riyad Mahrez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maguire, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Leicester \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maguire v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mahrez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maguire v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Maguire ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi\u201d, Mahrez n\u00f3i v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. \u201cK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Leicester v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi Maguire thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng Leicester c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i, v\u00ec th\u1ebf Maguire n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111ang th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Nh\u1eefng Phil Jones v\u00e0 Chris Smalling th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, Eric Bailly \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong khi Marcos Rojo hay Daley Blind kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez toi Arsenal\" title=\"Mahrez t\u1edbi Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/5/tan-binh-dau-tien-cua-man-city-o-he-2018-co-gia-60-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mahrez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Maguire, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhu c\u1ea7u t\u00ecm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David De Gea c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Maguire th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb thu ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMaguire n\u0103m nay 25 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i Sheffiled United. Sau 3 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho CLB qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh gia nh\u1eadp Hull City v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n sang Leicester m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ban \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 17 tri\u1ec7u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-lai-ga-gam-mu-mua-alderweireld-172-191095.html\">Tottenham l\u1ea1i g\u1ea1 g\u1eabm MU mua Alderweireld</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-mu-va-chelsea-dai-chien-vi-bonucci-172-191094.html\">PSG, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao kh\u1ee7ng AC Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh-172-191089.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201csao b\u1ef1\u201d Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu-172-191059.html\">Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau MU sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4197","checkdouble":"191122"},{"date":"23:19 13/07","title":"Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u: Tam t\u1ea5u k\u1ebb \u1edf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/liverpool-toi-my-du-dau-tam-tau-ke-o-nguoi-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu Roberto Firmino v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Salah v\u00e0 Mane tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 Senegal. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, Salah v\u00e0 Mane \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y khi The Kop sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Salah b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi Uruguay do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai v\u00e0 h\u1ecd thua 0-1. 2 tr\u1eadn sau, m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n song \u201cC\u00e1c Pharaoh\u201d v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Salah-va-Mane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah v\u00e0 Mane c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Mane, Senegal c\u1ee7a Anh th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 thi\u1ebfu Firmino</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Liverpool s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup v\u1edbi Dortmund, Man City v\u00e0 Man United. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e1 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 Torino v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roberto Firmino chan thuong\" title=\"Roberto Firmino ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/neville-khuyen-mu-chieu-mo-sao-khung-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Firmino v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean v\u00e0o s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool m\u1edbi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Roberto Firmino. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f9ng \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 bao g\u1ed3m Jordan Henderson v\u00e0 Trent Alexander-Arnold (Anh), Simon Mignolet (B\u1ec9) v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren (Croatia). H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi West Ham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 12/8.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-mung-ro-voi-man-trinh-dien-cua-2-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-190681.html\">Klopp m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a 2 t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam-172-190673.html\">Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir-172-190670.html\">Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4196","checkdouble":"191136"},{"date":"05:58 14/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 Xherdan Shaqiri sau khi k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Stoke City.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n Xherdan Shaqiri ra \u0111i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y v\u1ed1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra, sau khi Stoke City c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi ngay sau World Cup 2018 chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 23 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf s\u00e2n Anfield, Shaqiri h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, anh lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d \u2013 T\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i n\u0103m 2014 khi Bayern Munich kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n anh cho Liverpool, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i sai l\u1ea7m sang Inter Milan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t HLV tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c cho Liverpool gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u danh gi\u00e1 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Chinh-thuc-Liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-Xherdan-Shaqiri-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mua Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Shaqiri tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb CLB qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Basel tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Inter Milan v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 2015. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i lang b\u1ea1t sang Anh gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t Stoke khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i tr\u1ea3i qua ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ed3i sinh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xherdan Shaqiri tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 sau hai qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 khu v\u1ef1c trung tuy\u1ebfn - Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u00e0 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/xherdan-shaqiri-va-tinh-yeu-voi-hai-mau-co-389-190288.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/xherdan-shaqiri-va-tinh-yeu-voi-hai-mau-co.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/xherdan-shaqiri-va-tinh-yeu-voi-hai-mau-co-389-190288.html\">Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi hai m\u00e0u c\u1edd</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o t\u00f4i c\u00f2n 16 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1eaft c\u1ecf trong v\u01b0\u1eddn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 n\u0103m 18 tu\u1ed5i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi Nam Phi d\u1ef1 World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4195","checkdouble":"191137"},{"date":"12:49 13/07","title":"N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 N\u1eef Myanmar (KT): Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u1ea1ng 3 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-myanmar-16h00-ngay-hom-nay-137.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 4-3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM 3-0 N\u1eee MYANMAR\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/175441-Highlight-Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: Tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. Hai b\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0103n mi\u1ebfng tr\u1ea3 mi\u1ebfng. \u01afu th\u1ebf h\u01a1i nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 10: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM M\u1ede T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a \u01b0u th\u1ebf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. S\u1ed1 7 Tuy\u1ebft Dung ph\u00e1 b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb lao v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ed3i b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-10.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 12: N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Myanmar th\u00ec s\u1ed1 23 Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ef3nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng dem v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u0103ng kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-12.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 15: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1eeb s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng bay ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n trong gang t\u1ea5c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-15.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 19: S\u1ed1 8 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba n\u1eef Myanmar r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u0103ng song kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-19.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 22: N\u1eef Myanmar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1 ly xa n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 29: Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. N\u1eef Myanmar c\u1ed1 t\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u00f2n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 31: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00fat v\u1ecdt x\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 36: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y sau c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u1eef Myanmar t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-38.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 41: Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, \u01b0u th\u1ebf n\u1eb1m trong tay tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Hi\u1ec7p 1 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat d\u00e0nh cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 Tuy\u1ebft Dung, ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 47: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo v\u00e0o trong cho Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 54: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. N\u1eef Myanmar c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-53.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 58: Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Li\u1ec5u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Myanmar.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-58.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 62: Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, Ph\u1ea1m H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat g\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-62.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 69: C\u00c1CH BI\u1ec6T \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C GIA T\u0102NG. Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb V\u00e2n v\u1eeba v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n solo \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf 2-3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-69.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 70: TR\u1eacN \u0110\u1ea4U AN B\u00c0I. Ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 1 ph\u00fat sau, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea1m H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn v\u1edbi pha kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, x\u1eed l\u00fd g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng r\u1ed3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1ed1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Myanmar.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-71.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 75: N\u1eef Myanmar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp trong khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 80: Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 an b\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong khi n\u1eef Myanmar c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 89: N\u1eef Myanmar kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m sao ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 v\u1eeba b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-Nu-Myanmar-88.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4194","checkdouble":"191100"},{"date":"14:54 13/07","title":"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/tuong-lai-gdkt-gede-sap-duoc-vff-dinh-doat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi G\u0110KT ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Jurgen Gede theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.</h2><h2>VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/19/Tuong-lai-GDKT-Jurgen-Gede-sap-duoc-VFF-dinh-doat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng Jurgen Gede l\u00e0m G\u0110KT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2016 theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m. B\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng trong c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua, G\u0110KT Jurgen Gede \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 &nbsp;VCK U20 World Cup, U15 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U15 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 qu\u00e2n VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a VFF. V\u00e0 sau 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, \u00f4ng Gede \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VFF gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng khi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gede v\u00e0 VFF s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n trong th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, sau khi \u00f4ng Gede tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c &ldquo;ch\u1ed1t&rdquo; h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gi\u1eefa G\u0110KT Gede v\u00e0 VFF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, G\u0110KT Gede s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch l\u1edbn trong 2 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018, AFF Cup 2018 v\u00e0 VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4193","checkdouble":"191108"},{"date":"15:55 13/07","title":"N\u00f3ng: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u2018Messi Th\u00e1i Lan\u2019","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/3/nong-doi-bong-nhat-ban-chinh-thuc-mua-dut-messi-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Consadole Sapporo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Consadole Sapporo&nbsp;</span>ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chanathip Songkrasin t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB Consadole Sapporo t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7/2017 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i.&nbsp;T\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi Jay&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Chanathip Songkrasin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/3/them-cau-thu-thai-lan-ghi-ban-o-giai-jleague-1-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chanathip ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Consadole Sapporo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 1 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J1 League, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0&nbsp;ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n trong 14 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho&nbsp;Consadole&nbsp;\u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa Consadole Sapporo v\u1edbi Consadole Sapporo, Chanathip ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Consadole v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110N\u00c1 n\u00e0y, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Muangthong United. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 song ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Muangthong United s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 570 ngh\u00ecn USD (13,1 t\u1ec9&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed3ng) t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Chanathip. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Consadole Sapporo mua \u0111\u1ee9t, Chanathip \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i J-League 1. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4192","checkdouble":"191109"}]}